text.tspan: May be played by any power to move this
marker to a new position on either side on
the colony display. During the Card Draw
phase of subsequent turns, No Effect results
from any colony of the chosen player are
converted to Card (if marker on Colonial
Governor side) or Elim (if marker on
Native Uprising side). Marker is removed
from display at the end of the Card Draw
phase in which a No Effect result is altered
(though it can return if this card is played
